                                <date>1958</date>. С. <biblScope unit="page">??–??</biblScope>.</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><encodingDesc><tagsDecl>&amp;renditions;</tagsDecl></encodingDesc></teiHeader><text><body><entry xml:id="entry_ævælmon" xml:lang="os"><form type="lemma"><orth>ævælmon</orth></form><sense><sense><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>без заботы доставшийся</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>one that was got without troubles</q></tr></sense><sense><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>легкий</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>easy</q></tr></sense></sense><re><form type="lemma"><orth>ævælmony fos</orth></form><sense><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>легкая нажива</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>easy profit</q></tr></sense></re><exampleGrp><example><quote>bīræǧtæ dyn qædy astæw ævælmony fos yssardtoj</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>волки посреди леса нашли легкую добычу</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>wolves found an easy prey in the middle of the forest</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_СОПам."/><biblScope>III 100</biblScope></bibl></example><example><quote>ævælmon fælloj ærxaston</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>я принес богатство, (доставшееся) без труда</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>I brought an easy money</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Čerm."/><biblScope>134</biblScope></bibl></example></exampleGrp><exampleGrp><example><quote>bīræǧtæ dyn qædy astæw ævælmony fos yssardtoj</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>волки посреди леса нашли легкую добычу</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>wolves found an easy prey in the middle of the forest</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_СОПам."/><biblScope>III 100</biblScope></bibl></example><example><quote>ævælmon fælloj ærxaston</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>я принес богатство, (доставшееся) без труда</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>I brought an easy money</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Čerm."/><biblScope>134</biblScope></bibl></example></exampleGrp><etym xml:lang="ru">Из %iæ-fælmon%i, где <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æ-"/> — негативная частица, а %ifælmon%i (отдельно не употребляется) восходит к <mentioned xml:lang="x-oldirn"><lang/> <w>*pari-man</w></mentioned> от %iman%i- ‘думать’, ‘заботиться’ и пр.; ср. <mentioned xml:lang="xpr"><lang/> <w>*parmāng(prmʽng)</w> <gloss><q>мысль</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><author>Henning,</author><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_SPAW"/><biblScope>1934, стр. 905</biblScope></bibl>). Тот же корень %iman%i- ‘думать’ в другом сложении находим в <mentioned xml:lang="os"><lang/> <w>fæsmon</w> <gloss><q>раскаяние</q></gloss></mentioned> q. v. Ср. также <ref type="xr" target="#entry_mondag"/>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">From %iæ-fælmon%i, where <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æ-"/> is a negative particle and %ifælmon%i (is not used separately) ttraces back to <mentioned xml:lang="x-oldirn"><lang/> <w>*pari-man</w></mentioned> from %iman%i- ‘to think’, ‘to care’ etc.; compare <mentioned xml:lang="xpr"><lang/> <w>*parmāng(prmʽng)</w> <gloss><q>thought</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><author>Henning,</author><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_SPAW"/><biblScope>1934, стр. 905</biblScope></bibl>). The same root %iman%i- ‘to think’ is found in <mentioned xml:lang="os"><lang/> <w>fæsmon</w> <gloss><q>repentance</q></gloss></mentioned> q. v. Compare also <ref type="xr" target="#entry_mondag"/>.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>